================================================================================================
JSONWorldBuilder v0.11
README
================================================================================================


================================================================================================
About:
------------------------
 - JSONWorldBuilder is a 2D level editor built using Titanium Desktop, JSON, HTML5 and JQuery.
 - It is designed for iOS development.
 - Features Include:
    - PLIST support
    - Multiple layers
    - Points, Lines and Polygons
    - Metadata
    - Tiled PNGs
    - Polygon PNG Masks
    - Unlimited Canvas Size
    - Image flipping
    - Zooming
    - Undo/redo stack
    - Small map file size (JSON)
 - JSONWorldBuilder also includes:
    - Baseball roster editor (designed for Golden Age Baseball TBA iOS game)
    - Animation editor
================================================================================================


================================================================================================
News (updated 5/3/2012):
------------------------
I'm finally working on a commercial iOS game. So, this 2D level editor will see a bunch of 
improvements over the next few months.
